Summary:	Calculating the time-evolution of the level-set equation with Octave
Name:		octave-%{octpkg}
Version:	0.3.0
Release:	1
Source0:	http://downloads.sourceforge.net/octave/%{octpkg}-%{version}.tar.gz
License:	GPLv3+
Group:		Sciences/Mathematics
